## 12. SPRINT 1 SCOPE — build only this

1. backend/db/001_initial_schema.sql — PostgreSQL schema with RLS
2. backend/core/ — config, auth middleware, logging
3. backend/main.py — FastAPI skeleton
4. backend/api/v1/routes/apps.py + runs.py
5. backend/api/v1/models/ — Pydantic schemas
6. backend/services/pipeline_service.py — stub wrapping agent/
7. backend/worker/tasks.py — Celery task scaffold
8. frontend skeleton — login, dashboard, run status, results pages

PRD generator, competitor comparison, trend tracking = Sprint 2.
Do not scaffold them in Sprint 1.
Ask before generating more than 150 lines in a single file.
